					<div class="answer collapse" id="question_1">
						<p>Our Customer Happiness team is based out of our Toronto, Canada head office with partial support available through our offices in Nottingham, UK and Melbourne, Australia. The team's hours of service are Monday to Friday from 9:30 AM to 5 PM EST (excluding holidays). We have limited support available on the weekends.
