					<h3>
						<button aria-controls="question_2" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_2" data-toggle="collapse">When can I expect a response to my email?</button>
					</h3>
					<div class="answer collapse" id="question_2">
						<p>Our team is working very hard but we are experiencing very rapid growth at this time. While we are expanding our resources, our aim is to respond to all inquiries within 48 hours. Please note that our response times may vary during peak periods such as after product launches or promotions.</p>
