					<div class="answer collapse js-shipping_restrictions" id="question_99">
						<p>If UPS was unable to deliver your parcel to the provided address, it may have been redirected to a nearby UPS Access Point for collection. Please check your delivery details for the Access Point location and collect your parcel as soon as possible.</p>
						<p>To collect your parcel:</p>
