						<button aria-controls="question_40" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_40" data-toggle="collapse">What methods of payment do you currently accept?</button>
					</h3>
					<div class="answer collapse" id="question_40">
						<p>We accept all major credit cards. When paying by credit card, your name and billing address must match the address on file with the card issuer. We also accept PayPal and credit card gift cards. Credit card gift cards can only be redeemed for orders less than the full amount available on the credit card gift card. We do not accept online payments from digital banking apps such as Revolut, Monzo, etc.</p>
