					</h3>
					<div class="answer collapse" id="question_currency_charge">
						<p>We currently offer prices in the following currencies which reflect pricing in each region. Some regions include taxes and duties while others do not. Our system takes into account these variations when checking out.Currently, our system provides pricing based on your shipping country:</p>
