					</h3>
					<div class="answer collapse" id="question_44">
						<p>We only charge the amount calculated during checkout and displayed on your invoice. However, if you are using a prepaid card, there may be temporary holds or fees associated with card usage. Please refer to the terms and conditions of the card you are using for further details. If you are not using a prepaid card and believe you have been overcharged, please do <a href="https://theordinary.com/on/demandware.store/Sites-deciem-us-Site/en_US/Link-Page?cid=contact-us">contact us</a> and we'll be happy to assist you.</p>
