						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_112" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_112" data-toggle="collapse">I'd like to return a product that was purchased via TikTok Shop.</button>
						</h3>
						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_112">
							<p>If you would like to return a product purchased via TikTok Shop, please be sure to explore their return policy, under section 4: <a href="https://shop-academy-us.tiktok.com/university/essay?knowledge_id=10013377&from=policy&role=1&identity=1">TikTok
                                    Shop Return Policy</a>

							</p>
						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_113" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_113" data-toggle="collapse">Can I cancel my TikTok Shop order?</button>
						</h3>
						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_113">
							<p>You have one (1) hour to cancel your TikTok Shop order via the TikTok Shop Portal. Kindly note that our Customer Happiness team is unable to cancel TikTok Shop orders on your behalf.</p>
						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_114" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_114" data-toggle="collapse">I have a question about a product purchased through TikTok Shop.</button>
						</h3>
						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_114">
							<p>Of course! Please feel free to contact our Customer Happiness team via our Contact Forms, Phone, and Live Chat. A member of our team will get back to you during working hours.</p>
						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_115" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_115" data-toggle="collapse">Why was my TikTok Shop order cancelled?</button>
						</h3>
						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_115">
							<p>We're sorry to hear about that! There are a number of reasons why a TikTok Shop order would be cancelled, kindly refer to your TikTokShop cancellation email for more information.</p>
						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_116" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_116" data-toggle="collapse">I'm having an issue with the TikTok Shop application. What should I do?</button>
