					<h2 class="faq-content-title" id="subscriptions">Subscriptions</h2>
					<div class="faq-content-section">
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_110" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_110" data-toggle="collapse">How do subscriptions work?</button>
						</h3>
						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_110">
							<p>When ordering your products from The Ordinary, you can now choose to have your products automatically shipped and delivered on your schedule by choosing your preferred frequency. You don&rsquo;t have to worry about running out of your favourites, and you can pause deliveries or cancel at any time without any hassle.</p>
						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_111" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_111" data-toggle="collapse">What are the benefits of subscribing?</button>
						</h3>
						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_111">
							<p>Receive 10% off plus free shipping with all subscription orders.</p>
						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_112" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_112" data-toggle="collapse">Is there a minimum commitment period?</button>
						</h3>
						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_112">
							<p>No. You can manage your subscription or cancel any time from your account.</p>
						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_113" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_113" data-toggle="collapse">How do I modify my delivery frequency?</button>
						</h3>
						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_113">
							<p>You can modify the delivery frequency of your subscription by visiting your account page. Just click on your subscription, change the &ldquo;sending every&rdquo; field by picking your desired frequency from the dropdown menu.</p>
						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_114" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_114" data-toggle="collapse">How do I cancel my subscription?</button>
						</h3>
						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_114">
							<p>To cancel your subscription, visit your account. On the &ldquo;Subscribe & Save&rdquo; tab, scroll to &ldquo;Upcoming Shipments&rdquo; to view your existing subscription orders. You can then cancel your desired subscription.</p>
						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_115" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_115" data-toggle="collapse">I&rsquo;ve cancelled my subscription but I also want to cancel my upcoming order. What are the next steps?</button>
						</h3>
						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_115">
							<p>If you wish to modify, skip or cancel an upcoming subscription order before your next order is shipped, you must do so at least 24 hours before your next order shipment date. Once your order has been processed for shipment, you will not be able to change your order.</p>
						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_116" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_116" data-toggle="collapse">Do I need to be logged into my DECIEM account to activate subscriptions?</button>
						</h3>
						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_116">
							<p>Yes. If you do not have an account, you will need to create one.</p>
						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_117" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_117" data-toggle="collapse">What countries are subscriptions available in?</button>
