						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_118" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_118" data-toggle="collapse">Can I pause or skip my next order?</button>
						</h3>
						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_118">
							<p>Yes, you can manage your subscription by visiting your account and selecting &ldquo;Subscribe & Save&rdquo;. You&rsquo;ll need to navigate to &ldquo;Upcoming Shipments.&rdquo; Once there, click &ldquo;Skip Order&rdquo; on the order you want to skip.</p>
						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_119" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_119" data-toggle="collapse">Can I receive my next order sooner?</button>
						</h3>
						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_119">
							<p>Yes, you can manage your subscription by visiting your account and selecting:</p>
							<ol>
								<li>&ldquo;Subscribe & Save&rdquo;</li>
								<li>Navigate to &ldquo;Upcoming Shipments&rdquo;.</li>
								<li>Select &ldquo;Send Now&rdquo; for the order to be processed.</li>
								<li>We&rsquo;ll ship the order as soon as possible.</li>
							</ol>
							<p>&nbsp;</p>
						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_120" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_120" data-toggle="collapse">What products within The Ordinary are available with subscriptions? / Are any products excluded from subscriptions?</button>
