						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_122" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_122" data-toggle="collapse">What is your return policy for subscriptions?</button>
						</h3>
						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_122">
							<p>We offer a 365-day return policy for our products, including products ordered through a subscription. Please visit our <a href="http://theordinary.com/returns">return policy</a> for additional details.</p>
