						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_123">
							<p>No, you will need to place a separate order.</p>
						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_124" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_124" data-toggle="collapse">Will I be notified if my card was declined for my subscription?</button>
						</h3>
						<div class="answer collapse" id="question_124">
							<p>Yes, if your card is declined you will receive an email prompting you to update the payment method through your account.</p>
						</div>
						<h3>
							<button aria-controls="question_125" aria-expanded="false" class="faq-content-toggler icon-right_chevron collapsed" data-target="#question_125" data-toggle="collapse">How do I update my subscription payment method?</button>
